All Implemented Interfaces:
Component, Service, ServiceProvider, QueueProviderService, SendQueueProviderService, GenericStateModel
public class SendQueueFactory
extends AspectFactory
implements ServiceProvider, SendQueueProviderService

This ServiceProvider provides and implements the SendQueueProviderService. Its jobs is to find or make a SendQueue for a given address. For now all addresses use a singleton queue, in order to enforce ordering across senders.
